A cozy evening scene in Studio Ghibli style: a whimsical workspace with an old wooden desk near a large window showing a twilight sky with soft clouds. On the desk, scattered fabric swatches and colorful paper patterns flutter gently, some pinned to a cork board. A vintage sewing mannequin draped with flowing, half-finished garments in rich jewel tones stands nearby. Warm golden light from a paper lantern illuminates jars of buttons, ribbons, and threads in every color. A content tabby cat curls up among the fabric scraps. The atmosphere is peaceful and creative, suggesting the joy of experimenting with different styles and designs, with that signature soft, dreamy Ghibli color palette of warm oranges, soft blues, and gentle greens.
